{c_label}Cooldown: {/c}{c_resource}{Cooldown Time}{/c} seconds
Aldkin channels a cone of flame for {c_number}{SF_2}{/c} seconds, repeatedly dealing {if:SF_11}{c_number}{payload:TOOLTIP_FLAME_DAMAGE}{/c}{else}moderate{/if} Fire damage.

Aldkin's Mercenary Core Skill alters his {c_important}Fate{/c} and Basic Attack.
{c_label}Fate:{/c} {c_important}Aflame{/c}
{c_label}Basic Attack:{/c} {c_important}Fire Shot{/c}
Aldkin hurls a flaming bolt at an enemy, dealing {if:SF_11}{c_number}{payload:MELEE_PAYLOAD_TOOLTIP}{/c} Fire damage and {c_number}{dot:BURNING_TOOLTIP}{/c} Burning damage over{else}light Fire damage and lightly Burning for{/if} {c_number}{SF_8}{/c} seconds.
